The game consists of a 5 by 5 grid of lights. When the game starts, some lights are switched on. Pressing any of the lights will toggle it and the four adjacent lights. The goal of the puzzle is to switch all the lights off, preferably in as few button presses as possible. Ludii allows 100 moves maximum before losing.
